<!--  5.3:  The encoding description                           -->

<!ELEMENT encodingDesc - - ((projectDesc)*, (samplingDecl)*,
(editorialDecl)*, (tagsDecl)?, (refsDecl)*, (classDecl)*, (p)*)>

<!ATTLIST encodingDesc 
